subject: Re:   Dear
body:
Dear Mr. Phillip Owens,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I hope you are doing well. Regarding the copy of my applied passport, I just wanted to confirm a few details before proceeding. Could you please provide me with some more information about the process and why it is taking longer than expected? Additionally, could you let me know if there are any fees or documents required for obtaining the copy?

I appreciate your assistance in this matter.

Best wishes,
Dixie
